Path-Class-Iterator version 0.02
================================

Walk a directory structure using an iterator.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Iterator
  Path::Class
  Class::Accessor::Fast
  IO::Dir

